niface_104ppx1665702659292.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ppx1665702659292.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ppx1665702659292.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ppx1665702659292\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Move files from a source to target directory or zip file.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__topic_d176987e1_d176988e1_d176989e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__p_d176990e1_d176991e1_d176992e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Switches</var>} <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">move</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>{+ <var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>}{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Destination</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Options</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__section_ttf_r51_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549093e78\">Switches and Parameters </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fpl1665702658861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpl1665702658861.html\" title=\"Executable for the Uniface Resource Manager, a command line utility for creating and manipulating Uniface archive files and other resources, files and DBMS tables.\">urm</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__section_ozq_s51_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549093e94\">Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__1\">Option</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-silent</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__2\">Move files silently, without displaying\n                        messages.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-noSubDir</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__2\">Do not process subdirectories</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-after=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">yyyymmdd</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">hhnnss</var>} |\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">today</code>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-before=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">yyyymmdd</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">hhnnss</var>} |\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">today</code>\n</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ppx1665702659292__table_d18653e1_d18654e1_d18655e1__entry__2\">Specify date of files.<p class=\"p\">The following\n                           separators are allowed: <code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code> (hyphen), <code class=\"ph codeph\">/</code>\n                           (slash), and <code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code> (colon).</p><div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__note_w5763ab1b5b1b1b7b5b3b2_w5764ab1b5b1b1b7b5b3_w5765ab1b5b1b1b7b5_w5766ab1b5b1b1b7_w5767ab1b5b1b1_w5768ab1b5b1_w5769ab1b5_w5770ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The date format differs from the\n      date format in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef</span> switches.</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__section_swf_551_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549093e199\">Example: Moving Objects</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__p_d177005e1_d177006e1_d177007e1\">The following command moves the specified files in\n            a directory, ignoring any subdirectories</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ppx1665702659292__pre_qgy_bms_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm move C:/Dir/FIL*.fil C:/NewDir/FIL*.fil -nosubdir</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531013\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531013\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "urm move Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Move files from a source to target directory or zip file. urm { Switches } move Source {+ Source }{ Destination } { Options } Switches and Parameters See urm . Options Option Description -silent Move files silently, without displaying messages. -noSubDir Do not process subdirectories -after= yyyymmdd { hhnnss } | today -before= yyyymmdd { hhnnss } | today Specify date of files. The following separators are allowed: - (hyphen), / (slash), and : (colon). Note: The date format differs from the date format in the /aft and /bef switches. Example: Moving Objects The following command moves the specified files in a directory, ignoring any subdirectories urm move C:/Dir/FIL*.fil C:/NewDir/FIL*.fil -nosubdir Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}